{
  "stem": "14251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on the-- in the corridor of that attic, my-- when my mother and father went through that-- and of course, we were covered with soot from that ash and debris there that had been piled up against there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As I was coming out of there sort of haltingly, that man, who was probably just somebody doing a repair there-- it wasn't Maletski.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had evaporated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "His role had been fulfilled, and his reward would be forthcoming surely.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This other little man said, now, [NON-ENGLISH], just sort of stunned to see a child emerging from this hole, which meant, well, come on out, little one.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He couldn't believe what he was seeing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But you see, he could have had he  been made of the same stuff as Mr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Maletski, said, here they are making a run for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It took some time for us to find out that they were not even looking for us yet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were caught in a situation where it was the Levents that they were looking for.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were not even searching for us just yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We would have just been caught up in the web.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The man did nothing and just walked away, fortunately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So there you have a case of people being good and innocent maybe surprised had no ax to grind with anyone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My father picked me up, and they ran for the nearest elevator-- there was an elevator that came right up to there-- instead of going through all those-- the square with the four doors, which still would lead you down into the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we went on the elevator, and I remember being carried and hurrying, always hurrying, stairs, this, that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was the same on attic day.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
